@startuml sequence_ambassador_application
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ambassador Application Flow (L2-018, L2-078)

actor Visitor
participant "AmbassadorPage\n/ambassador" as Page
participant "Content API" as Content
participant "AmbassadorForm\nComponent" as Form
participant "POST\n/api/inquiries" as API
database "inquiries.inquiries" as DB

== Page Load ==
Visitor -> Page: Navigate to /ambassador
Page -> Content: GET program content
Content --> Page: Benefits, requirements,\ntestimonials
Page --> Visitor: Program info + form

== Application Submit ==
Visitor -> Form: Fill extended fields:\nname, email, phone,\nInstagram, follower count,\nwhy join
Visitor -> Form: Submit
Form -> Form: Zod validate\n(required fields check)
Form -> API: POST {\n  name, email,\n  subject: "[AMBASSADOR APPLICATION]",\n  message: { fullName, phone,\n    instagram, tiktok,\n    followerCount, whyJoin },\n  category: "ambassador"\n}
API -> DB: INSERT inquiry\n(status: "pending")
DB --> API: Inquiry row
API --> Form: 201 Created
Form --> Visitor: "Application submitted!\nWe'll review and contact you."

@enduml
